when you tag an entry you need to follow the following structure: `:one_main_tag:UPPERCASE_CONTEXT_LABEL:regular_tag1:regular_tag2:` here is one example for a context that is about my nixos environment =:<sub>c</sub>:NIXOS

tags will be separated into 3 groups;

1.  main tags
2.  context label tags
3.  regular tags
